<div id="pf465c" class="pf w66 h2f7" data-page-no="465c"><div class="pc pc465c w66 h2f7"><div class="t m26c x8 h5 y2f7d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 13 September 21-27 </div><div class="t m1cca x4a h5e y2c4d ff4 fs25 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m2589 x14 h11 y2c4d ff4 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">171</div><div class="t m1870 x6f h11 y2c4d ff4 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t me1a x55 h11 y2c4d ff4 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">n2 </div><div class="t m89 xcf hc2 y2c65 ff1 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">51.aff2Erfing5 </div><div class="t m31b7 x16 h11 y2bb8 ff4 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.112m.115 </div><div class="t m58a x1cc h5 y23a5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Consider him who endured from </div><div class="t m288 x1cc h5 y2380 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">iners such hostility against himself, </div><div class="t m7a8 xd5 h5 y1627 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that you may not grow weary or </div><div class="t m220 x1cc h5 yf14 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">int-hearted. In your struggle against </div><div class="t m10a0 x1cc ha y207 ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">i </div><div class="t m6a6 xd1 h5 y18d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you have not yet resisted to the </div><div class="t me62 x1cc h5 y5cc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">)int of shedding your blood&quot; (Heb. </div><div class="t m16b x93 h5 y484 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">:3, 4, RSV). </div><div class="t m8d4 x93 h5 y11c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In a very real sense, Job was a type of </div><div class="t mad2 x93 h5 y557 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e suffering Saviour, and his </div><div class="t m37c x93 h5 y8e0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perience was an example of the </div><div class="t ma4 x1cc h5 y5d0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">introversy between Christ and </div><div class="t me81 x93 h5 y2d9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tan. </div><div class="t m6a2 x93 h5 y622 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Very early in the history of the </div><div class="t m33b x1cc h5 y244 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Drld is given the life record of one </div><div class="t mb97 x93 h5 yb1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">)b] over whom this controversy of </div><div class="t m654 xd6 h5 ye1a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tan&apos;s was </div><div class="t m1ce x48 h5 ye1a ff9 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">waged.&quot;—Education, </div><div class="t m791 x87 h5 ye1a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t m71a x93 h5 yfc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m2b0 x93 h5 y6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is altogether appropriate, at the </div><div class="t m1169 x93 h5 y2a1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3se of this series of lessons, to take a </div><div class="t m671 x93 h5 y1f7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ok at the great Sufferer of whom Job </div><div class="t m9be x93 h5 y8f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is a type. </div><div class="t m61b x93 h5 y22e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Christ&apos;s situation and Job&apos;s are </div><div class="t mf31 x93 h5 y34d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">uch alike. Job on his ash heap, Christ </div><div class="t m107e xd1 h5 y87c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His cross. Job bears the pain and </div><div class="t m5f9 x93 h5 y725 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e public reproach of black leprosy, </div><div class="t m3e6 x93 h5 y107 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Irist of crucifixion. Each is </div><div class="t m132f xd6 h5 y38e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rrounded by a jeering, irresponsible </div><div class="t m8b8 x93 h5 y2a5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bble. . . . </div><div class="t m37d xd6 h5 y134 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Christ suffers the same unjust </div><div class="t mff x93 h5 y234 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sapproval of the mob, &apos;His </div><div class="t m16f xd6 h5 y28f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pearance was . . . marred.&apos; Isaiah </div><div class="t mab2 xd6 h5 y94e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">:14. So each man, Job and the </div><div class="t m19b3 xd6 h5 ya3b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">aster, is accused of evil on the basis </div><div class="t m68f xd6 h5 yd6a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">at his physical condition testifies to </div><div class="t md1d x93 h5 ye07 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">raven&apos;s condemnation. . . . - </div><div class="t mdff xd6 h5 y73 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Like the mob which followed </div><div class="t m5e9 xd6 h5 y503 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Irist to His trial and to His </div><div class="t m624 xd6 h5 y443 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ucifixion, the people about Job exult </div><div class="t mae3 xd5 h5 yebd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the opportunity to mistreat a </div><div class="t m3aa xd6 h5 y7c0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perior. . . . </div><div class="t m8a0 xc4 h5 y328 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. . When Job intervenes for his </div><div class="t m13aa xd6 h5 y3c4 ff9 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ree </div><div class="t ma2 x3 h5 y3c4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">friends, who have augmented </div><div class="t m34b xd3 h5 y31 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sorrow as we sinners grieve our </div><div class="t m213 xd6 h5 ya1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ediator, his action becomes a high </div><div class="t m758 xd6 h5 y953 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Duntain of evidence that he is a type  </div><div class="t m58b x3c h5 y208e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ.... Job is </div><div class="t m2442 x8a h35 y208e ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a </div><div class="t m60c xa9 h5 y208e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mediator; Christ </div><div class="t m1ddc x3c h5 y237f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is </div><div class="t m7d0 x2b h5 y237f ff9 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the </div><div class="t m837 x21 h5 y2389 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mediator. </div><div class="t me5c x2b h5 y234f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Job&apos;s willingness to pray for his </div><div class="t m73d x3c h5 y2053 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">opponents climaxes his </div><div class="t m10f x3c h5 y1ec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">demonstration of loyalty to God. The </div><div class="t m57a x3c h5 y57d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accusations of these men have been </div><div class="t me47 x3c h5 ya6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">salt in his wounds. At the close of the </div><div class="t m37c x3c h5 y373 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ordeal his prayer in their behalf </div><div class="t m38a x3c h5 y14a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">foreshadows the Saviour&apos;s prayer from </div><div class="t m599 x3c h5 y854 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the cross, &apos;Father, forgive them; for </div><div class="t mda x3c h5 yd3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">they know not what they do.&apos; Luke </div><div class="t m6bf x3c h5 y2d8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">23:34. Thus Job prays for his </div><div class="t md30 x3c h5 y25f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persecutors .&quot;—Pau IT. Gibbs, </div><div class="t m57b xca h5 y25f ff9 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job </div><div class="t m3b4 x160 h35 y25f ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t m34a x3c h5 y1b5 ff9 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the </div><div class="t m1b3 x45 h35 ya25 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mysteries of Wisdom, </div><div class="t mbb2 xbb h5 y1b5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 138-140. </div><div class="t m842 x1f h5 y210 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our lesson this week we look at </div><div class="t m119f x3c h5 y285 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus to see the suffering He passed </div><div class="t m27c x3c h5 y485 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through while achieving our salvation. </div><div class="t m21d x3c h5 y34b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He left heaven and came down to this </div><div class="t m134e x5c h5 y179 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">earth to become a man and to live as a </div><div class="t m9f1 x5c h5 ya82 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man. </div><div class="t m308 x2b h5 yda6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He came to His own creation, to His </div><div class="t m1a3 x5c h5 y438 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">own chosen people; yet He was </div><div class="t m17f x5c h5 y5b6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rejected and despised. And in </div><div class="t m6d7 x5c h5 y43a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gethsemane He suffered the </div><div class="t m5af x5c h5 y31c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">separation from His Father. </div><div class="t m829 x1f h5 y268 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On the cross we have the supreme </div><div class="t m14c x5c h5 y55d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">example of sacrifice. When we </div><div class="t m681 x5c h5 y1a3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognize that Jesus did all this so that </div><div class="t m147 x5c h5 y91b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you and I can be saved, our hearts melt </div><div class="t m442 x5c h5 y134 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in love. The suffering that Jesus </div><div class="t m57f x5c h5 y421 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">endured for us is called to mind by the </div><div class="t m60e x5c h5 y28e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">feet-washing service and the bread </div><div class="t m2ef x5c h5 y94e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and wine of the Lord&apos;s Supper. </div><div class="t m14a x5c h5 y251 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x5c h5 y99 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m211 x8f h5 ye07 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Became Man </div><div class="t m648 x8f h5 y73 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gal. 4:4, 5) </div><div class="t m558 x5c h5 y503 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m3a8 x8f h5 y503 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Lived As Man </div><div class="t m24e x8f h5 y443 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Heb. 2:16, 17) </div><div class="t mb7 x5c h5 y5bc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m245 x8f h5 yebd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Suffered and </div><div class="t m1584 x8f h5 y7c0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Died As Man </div><div class="t m302 x8f h5 y715 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 1:11) </div><div class="t m1ce x5c h5 y560 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m2a6 x8f h5 y560 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Symbol of Humiliation </div><div class="t m674 x8f h5 y31 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 13:12) </div><div class="t m8a8 x5c h5 yf2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m71a x8f h5 y880 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Symbol of a Body </div><div 